T1  - Investment in technological innovations: An option pricing approach
AU  - Grenadier, Steven R.
AU  - Weiss, Allen M.
JO  - Journal of Financial Economics
VL  - 44
IS  - 3
SP  - 397
EP  - 416
PY  - 1997
DA  - 1997/06/01/
